<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="c14Mar1933"><font color="red">14 March 1933</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver): Mr Joyce &hellip; very pale indeed &hellip; still extremely nervous &hellip; He has started work on overhauling the fragments of the second part and I do think that work will take his mind from his family affairs. </div>
